SELECT - to select data from database


SELECT * FROM TableName

* - everything
DISTINCT - Different values


SELECT column1, column2, column3
FROM TableName;

This will select Columns 1, 2 and 3 (Fields 1,2,3) from the table.

Q. statement to get all the columns from the Customers table.
SELECT * FROM Customers

Q. Write a statement that will select the City column from the Customers table.
SELECT City FROM Customers;
